[[File:Yggdrasil2Hades.jpg|right|thumb|300px|The layers of Hades, Mount Olympus, and Yggdrasil]]
{{Main|Afterlife}}
Most souls that arrived in Hades became [[Soul larva|larvae]]&mdash;sickly, human-headed worm-spirits&mdash;that were harvested by the night hags as a commodity for Lower Plane commerce.
